message:
@PhillyJeff I have a feeling you're mixing theories here, just a bit. 

Many theories would say that a story is a Stasis, followed by an Inciting Incident, and then things play out until a new Stasis is achieved.

Dramatica doesn't really look at stories that way, and even though we still talk about inciting incidents, perhaps it would be better to ask you what the earliest occurrence of the Driver is.
